Package hms.admin

Class Administrator

Object
Staff
Administrator
All Implemented Interfaces:
User
public class Administrator extends Staff implements User
Represents an Administrator in the Hospital Management System (Hms) Inherits from Staff and implements the User interface Provides functionalities for managing hospital staff, appointments, and inventory
